	<h6>Lokon Academy Exchange Program</h6>
    <p>
    Lokon Academy provides the opportunity for you to study in Singapore and yet still remain as a Indonesia based student paying your fees in Indonesia currency.<br>
    This is a unique program in Asia and is only able to operate because the academy operates across both countries.<br>
    The program is designed to ensure you get the best possible outcomes from your years of study with the academy.
    </p>
    <h6>Trimester System</h6>
    <p>With a trimester program, you can complete your High School in 2 years.</p>
    <h6>Supportive study environment</h6>
    <p>
    Our academy is designed to support collaborative learning and collaborative study techniques.<br>
    We provide you with access to a full range of facilities and services to support your learning.<br>
    These include dormitory, laundry, dining hall library and associated study facilities, computer laboratories, chemistry lab, and biology lab. Additionally, you will have access to a range of sporting facilities and can join a number of clubs and societies.<br>
    We aim to provide a full academy experience and not just a study program.
